<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk.Razor">

	<PropertyGroup>
		<TargetFramework>net10.0</TargetFramework>
		<Nullable>enable</Nullable>
		<ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>

		<!-- NuGet Package Metadata -->
		<PackageId>BlazorRTE</PackageId>
		<Version>1.1.2</Version>
		<Authors>simscon1</Authors>
		<Company>LoneWorx LLC</Company>
		<Product>BlazorRTE</Product>
		<Description>Professional rich text editor for Blazor with 51 features, full ARIA implementation, emoji support (1800+ emojis), 27 keyboard shortcuts, zero JavaScript dependencies, 54 passing unit tests, professional SVG icons, built-in XSS protection, and dark mode. Native Blazor component. GPL v3 for open-source, commercial license coming soon.</Description>
		<PackageTags>blazor;rich-text-editor;wysiwyg;rte;editor;text-editor;emoji;emoji-picker;emoji-autocomplete;formatting;blazor-component;razor;contenteditable;gpl;accessibility;wcag;keyboard-shortcuts;testing;bunit;aria</PackageTags>
		<PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/simscon1/BlazorRTE</PackageProjectUrl>
		<RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/simscon1/BlazorRTE</RepositoryUrl>
		<RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
		<PackageLicenseExpression>GPL-3.0-or-later</PackageLicenseExpression>
		<PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
		<GeneratePackageOnBuild>false</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
		<PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>true</PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>
		<Copyright>Copyright (c) 2024-2026 LoneWorx LLC</Copyright>
		<PackageReleaseNotes><![CDATA[v1.1.2 Emoji Support, Bug Fixes & UX Improvements (2026-02-08)

ADDED:
- Emoji Picker with 1800+ searchable emojis
  - Organized by category (Smileys, Animals, Food, etc.)
  - Search by name or keyword
  - Recently used emojis (persisted)
  - Full keyboard navigation
  - Dark mode support
- Emoji Autocomplete - Type :smile for inline suggestions
  - Quick emoticons (:), :D, <3) for instant replacement
  - Full autocomplete (2+ chars) shows 10 best matches
  - Keyboard navigation (↑ ↓ Enter Esc)
  - Auto-positioning (viewport-aware)
- 27 Keyboard Shortcuts (Ctrl+B, Ctrl+I, Ctrl+K, Ctrl+Shift+E, etc.)
  - Formatting shortcuts (Bold, Italic, Underline, Strikethrough)
  - Heading shortcuts (Ctrl+Alt+0-3)
  - Font size shortcuts (Ctrl+Shift+> / <)
  - Lists, alignment, links, emoji picker
- 54 Unit Tests with 100% pass rate (bUnit + xUnit)
  - Component rendering & initialization
  - Accessibility (ARIA attributes, keyboard navigation)
  - Security (XSS prevention, HTML sanitization)
- Dynamic font size button - Shows current size at cursor position
  - Displays: 10, 14, 16, 18, 24, or 32
  - Updates in real-time when moving cursor
  - Matches industry standard behavior (Word, Google Docs)

FIXED:
- Link button now functional (prompts user for URL via browser dialog)
  - Validates text selection before allowing link creation
  - Auto-adds https:// prefix if missing
  - Shows "Remove link?" confirmation when cursor in existing link
  - Properly raises OnLinkCreated events
- Mouse click support for all pickers (was keyboard-only)
  - Added @onmousedown:stopPropagation to all 5 pickers
  - Fixes: Heading, Font Family, Font Size, Text Color, Highlight Color
  - Prevents toolbar's preventDefault from blocking picker clicks

ACCESSIBILITY:
- Improved ARIA semantics for link button
  - Changed from aria-pressed to aria-haspopup="dialog" (correct pattern)
  - Dynamic aria-label based on context ("Insert link" vs "Edit link")
- Complete ARIA implementation following WAI-ARIA 1.2 patterns
  - All pickers have proper role attributes (listbox/grid)
  - Color swatches use role="gridcell" with aria-label
  - Emoji autocomplete has role="listbox" with aria-selected states
  - Character count uses aria-live="polite"

QUALITY:
- All 54 unit tests passing
- Both keyboard and mouse interaction verified
- Event callbacks properly wired

See: https://github.com/simscon1/BlazorRTE/blob/master/Docs/CHANGELOG.md]]></PackageReleaseNotes>
		
		<PackageIcon>icon.png</PackageIcon>
		<IncludeSymbols>true</IncludeSymbols>
		<SymbolPackageFormat>snupkg</SymbolPackageFormat>
		<EmbedUntrackedSources>true</EmbedUntrackedSources>
		<PublishRepositoryUrl>true</PublishRepositoryUrl>
	</PropertyGroup>

	<ItemGroup>
	  <Content Include="icon.png">
	    <ExcludeFromSingleFile>true</ExcludeFromSingleFile>
	    <CopyToPublishDirectory>PreserveNewest</CopyToPublishDirectory>
	  </Content>
	</ItemGroup>

	<ItemGroup>
		<SupportedPlatform Include="browser" />
	</ItemGroup>

	<ItemGroup>
		<PackageReference Include="Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.Web" Version="10.0.2" />
	</ItemGroup>

	<!-- Include README and LICENSE in NuGet package -->
	<ItemGroup>
		<None Include="README.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
		<None Include="LICENSE.txt" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
		<None Include="icon.png" Pack="true" PackagePath="\" />
	</ItemGroup>
	<ItemGroup>
	  <ProjectReference Include="..\..\BlazorEmo.Solution\BlazorEmo\BlazorEmo.csproj" />
	</ItemGroup>
</Project>
